column5: Hi all, This happened to me yesterday while crappie fishing. What are the chances of that?!?VIDEOhttps://youtu.be/qrD7AauNARg
Had them go down the hole, but never able to grab them out of another hole. That's awesome!!

Yeah, definitely unusual. Just a guess - crappies taken deeper than around 18 ft tend to get the bends, and can be unable to get back down, so it is possible that it stayed pretty close to the surface, and just happened to squirm around in the direction of the other hole. Bill
